00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:53,420
Din! Go home.

253
00:17:53,420 --> 00:17:55,020
Get out.

254
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:57,360
I'll help them out. Come on.

255
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,582
Don't go to that dude.

256
00:17:59,582 --> 00:18:03,660
- Come on.
- Come on.

257
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:09,180
What should we do, Dad?

258
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:12,230
Done.

259
00:18:13,193 --> 00:18:15,893
Honey, it looks delicious.

260
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:26,060
Didn't you say we were going out to eat?

261
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:28,365
Why did you change your mind?

262
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:32,680
We can eat out whenever we want.

263
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:36,960
But it's difficult to eat the food you cook.

264
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:41,200
In that case,

265
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,760
