266
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:47,360
I'll cook for you every day.

267
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,620
I'll think about it.

268
00:18:53,820 --> 00:18:55,920
Don't think about it for too long.

269
00:18:57,645 --> 00:18:59,845
By the way,

270
00:18:59,845 --> 00:19:03,600
did you tell Kansinee that we were dating

271
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:09,080
because you wanted her to tell the chairwoman?

272
00:19:11,333 --> 00:19:13,533
Yes.

273
00:19:13,533 --> 00:19:16,760
I don't want to date you secretly.

274
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:19,411
It's like it's wrong for us to date.

275
00:19:19,411 --> 00:19:23,200
And I want her to know that I'm not afraid of her.

276
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:28,459
Don't worry.

277
00:19:28,459 --> 00:19:32,520
I promise I'll be there for you

278
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:35,200
no matter what happens.

279
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:39,010
I'll get her to accept that we're dating.

280
00:19:43,019 --> 00:19:45,619
Me, too.

281
00:19:45,619 --> 00:19:50,200
I won't give up or run away again.

282
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:54,400
In that case, we should

283
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:58,212
discuss how to deal with the chairwoman.

284
00:19:58,212 --> 00:20:00,320
After you finish your salmon,

285
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:04,200
go to Nannam's, pack your stuff, and move in with me.

286
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,860
So we can discuss the plan together.

287
00:20:06,860 --> 00:20:08,900
Are you worried I'll run away?

288
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:11,800
I don't like being alone.

289
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:14,660
I like being with you.

290
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:24,979
[Chanaratee]

291
00:20:24,979 --> 00:20:28,406
Hom? Why did she call you?

292
00:20:33,773 --> 00:20:36,773
Why are you so drunk, Din?

293
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:45,240
He's so drunk. I don't know what's bothering him.

294
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:48,500
I'm not drunk.

295
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:53,260
Why are you drunk?

296
00:20:58,359 --> 00:21:00,559
Why are you here?

297
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:07,940
Let's talk about it later.

298
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:10,500
Let's get Din up there now. Let's go.

299
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:14,880
Careful.

300
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:22,600
Hom, you can't go to that dude.

301
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:25,470
- Hom.
- I'm not Hom. I'm your brother.

302
00:21:25,470 --> 00:21:27,533
I'm your brother.

303
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:36,380
What are you talking about?

304
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:38,560
Ignore him.

305
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:42,880
I don't think he's talking nonsense.

306
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:48,920
If there's nothing else, I'll go home.

307
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:51,820
Okay, I'll come back with you.

308
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:53,420
I'll go back.

309
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:55,320
Wait.

310
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:58,280
Why don't you drive my car?

311
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,959
It's not safe for you to take a taxi back.

312
00:21:59,959 --> 00:22:01,800
It's all right.

313
00:22:01,800 --> 00:22:04,200
How are you going to work tomorrow?

314
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:06,450
I'll ask Mahakul to pick me up tomorrow.

315
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:08,040
Take it.

316
00:22:11,560 --> 00:22:15,260
Call me when you get there.

317
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:26,000
Hom, don't leave me.

318
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:38,380
Why are your muscles so strong? It's strange.

319
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:44,940
Okay, Khun Lom. I arrived.

320
00:22:47,593 --> 00:22:50,173
Okay, that's it.

321
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:57,360
You're finally dating Khun Sira, aren't you?

322
00:23:01,526 --> 00:23:04,032
Does Din know?

323
00:23:04,032 --> 00:23:05,932
I think he knows.

324
00:23:06,946 --> 00:23:12,146
Then... I think you had something to do with Din being drunk.

325
00:23:14,759 --> 00:23:15,960
I don't think so.

326
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:20,820
If that was the case, he should have come to me. But he went to you.

327
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:25,900
I think he wanted to stop you from dating Nannam.

328
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,497
I told you Din was talking nonsense.

329
00:23:27,497 --> 00:23:29,839
You're keeping something from me, aren't you?

330
00:23:31,372 --> 00:23:33,600
Don't try to change the subject.

331
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:37,540
I'm asking about you and Khun Sira.

332
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:43,020
If you're seeing him, what should you say to your mom...

333
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,738
about you going abroad?

334
00:23:45,738 --> 00:23:47,500
I haven't thought about it yet.

335
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:52,486
I'm thinking about how to get Khun Premyuda to accept us.

336
00:23:52,486 --> 00:23:55,640
It should be hard. You have to be mentally prepared.

337
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:59,920
Come on. Did you have to say that?

338
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:02,800
I have to get you mentally prepared.

339
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:04,972
I won't give up easily.

340
00:24:04,972 --> 00:24:06,420
Good.

341
00:24:06,420 --> 00:24:08,900
I'm waiting for your good news.

342
00:24:11,638 --> 00:24:14,653
Don't give up too easily.

343
00:24:14,653 --> 00:24:16,453
What?

344
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:19,680
About Din.

345
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:23,620
I'm waiting for you to marry Din.

346
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:25,593
Don't talk nonsense.

347
00:24:25,593 --> 00:24:27,593
It will never happen.

348
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:37,479
Din.

349
00:24:38,100 --> 00:24:39,600
Din.

350
00:24:44,033 --> 00:24:45,733
Wake up.

351
00:24:46,840 --> 00:24:48,540
Brother?

352
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:53,500
Why am I at your place?

353
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:56,279
Khun Chanaratee sent you here last night.

354
00:24:56,279 --> 00:24:58,120
Hom?

355
00:24:58,120 --> 00:25:00,340
Hom sent me here?

356
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:02,900
Did she see that dude?

357
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:05,600
How could she see him so late at night?

358
00:25:06,371 --> 00:25:07,780
What happened to you last night?

359
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:10,660
Why were you so drunk and messing around at Hom's house?

360
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:12,840
I didn't mess around.

361
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:15,786
I just wanted to make it clear to her.

362
00:25:15,786 --> 00:25:17,486
About what?

363
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:22,405
You don't want Khun Hom to see Nannam, do you?

364
00:25:22,405 --> 00:25:25,793
How do you know that? Did Hom tell you that?

365
00:25:25,793 --> 00:25:29,027
No. You said it.

366
00:25:30,006 --> 00:25:31,500
What?

367
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:35,280
Why don't you want Khun Hom to see Nannam?

368
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:36,760
I don't want it.

369
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:39,040
She's robbing the cradle.

370
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:41,533
That's her business.

371
00:25:41,533 --> 00:25:45,425
Why? I don't think you have the right to stop her.

372
00:25:45,425 --> 00:25:46,882
Don't I have the right to stop her?

373
00:25:46,882 --> 00:25:48,900
I have the right to stop her.

374
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,380
How come?

375
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:51,880
Well─

376
00:25:53,580 --> 00:25:55,738
I have the right to stop her anyway.

377
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,900
You don't have to pretend to sleep.

378
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:05,060
Tell me what you have done.

379
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:06,940
Brother, can you stop pushing me?

380
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:09,520
If you don't tell me,

381
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:13,494
I won't help you in the future.

382
00:26:13,494 --> 00:26:15,240
I'll leave your coffee here.

383
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:17,180
Wait, Brother. Calm down.

384
00:26:19,086 --> 00:26:21,300
I can say it.

385
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:23,560
But you should promise me

386
00:26:23,560 --> 00:26:27,580
you won't get angry when I tell you.

387
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:30,265
Come here. Don't run, Din.

388
00:26:30,265 --> 00:26:31,646
Stop!

389
00:26:31,646 --> 00:26:33,879
Din. Stop!

390
00:26:33,879 --> 00:26:36,042
Didn't you promise me that you wouldn't be angry? Why are you chasing me?

391
00:26:36,042 --> 00:26:38,863
Don't you think you deserve to be beaten?

392
00:26:38,863 --> 00:26:41,840
From now on, you're not allowed to drink. If you drink, this will happen again.

393
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:43,460
I didn't mean to do that.

394
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:47,220
If Hom hadn't messed with me, it wouldn't have happened.

395
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:51,320
How can you blame Hom?

396
00:26:51,320 --> 00:26:53,675
You have to take responsibility for that.

397
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,800
I want to take responsibility.

398
00:26:56,800 --> 00:27:00,880
I have tried to talk to Hom and solve it. But she keeps running away.

399
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,660
And then there's that dude.

400
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:04,840
You said you wanted to take responsibility.

401
00:27:04,840 --> 00:27:06,765
Is that because you feel guilty,

402
00:27:06,765 --> 00:27:10,665
or is it because you have a crush on Hom?

403
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:13,205
Brother, don't ask so much now. Okay?

404
00:27:13,205 --> 00:27:16,640
The unsolved problems are already giving me numerous headaches.

405
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:19,220
If you want to solve it,

406
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:22,640
you have to find the answer to it first.

407
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:25,760
So you will know how to take responsibility.

408
00:27:26,470 --> 00:27:27,980
[GU]

409
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:31,400
Did Din tell you what happened last night?

410
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:35,480
It's hot.

411
00:27:36,339 --> 00:27:37,760
Well.

412
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:41,540
Din asked me to give him some time, and then he would tell me.

413
00:27:45,072 --> 00:27:47,700
You are superb at stalling.

414
00:27:47,700 --> 00:27:50,786
You always stall.

415
00:27:50,786 --> 00:27:54,700
Hom is the same. She didn't say anything to me.

416
00:27:56,866 --> 00:27:59,446
I think we shouldn't worry about others.

417
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:02,980
We should focus on us.

418
00:28:03,520 --> 00:28:06,220
Did Khun Premyuda ask you

419
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:09,700
about our relationship?

420
00:28:09,700 --> 00:28:12,280
The chairwoman didn't say anything.

421
00:28:14,026 --> 00:28:15,623
Or does she not know?

422
00:28:15,623 --> 00:28:18,125
The whole mall knows it. How could she not know?

423
00:28:18,125 --> 00:28:21,000
Kansinee knows it. The chairwoman must know it.

424
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:23,620
It's so quiet.

425
00:28:23,620 --> 00:28:26,972
Maybe she's thinking of a plan to stab me in the back.

426
00:28:26,972 --> 00:28:29,580
The chairwoman is not that kind of person.

427
00:28:29,580 --> 00:28:31,940
If she's still so quiet,

428
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:36,440
I'll go and make it clear to her.

429
00:28:38,986 --> 00:28:42,300
Let me know if there's anything I can do to help.

430
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:47,460
You can...

431
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:51,340
cheer for me.

432
00:28:52,986 --> 00:28:54,486
Okay?

433
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:57,500
Cheer for me.

434
00:28:58,340 --> 00:29:01,159
Your illness is much better.

435
00:29:01,159 --> 00:29:05,140
Before, when you were touched by someone,

436
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:09,200
you would wipe it with a wet wipe.

437
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:13,260
I don't know how I got cured.

438
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:15,400
I should ask Dr. Zhao.

439
00:29:25,484 --> 00:29:27,520
It's enough for me to have you around.

440
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:31,600
Cutie.

441
00:29:36,126 --> 00:29:38,026
Maha.

442
00:29:40,086 --> 00:29:42,086
What is it, Maha?

443
00:29:44,059 --> 00:29:45,859
Where is Maha?

444
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:48,300
He went out.

445
00:29:48,300 --> 00:29:50,140
He saw it all.

446
00:29:53,115 --> 00:29:55,480
You.

447
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:58,386
You've developed a habit of lying.

448
00:29:58,386 --> 00:30:02,086
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

449
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:27,945
Kheetika high-profilely announced a relationship with Khun Sira.

450
00:30:27,945 --> 00:30:29,900
Aren't you going to do something?

451
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:31,540
What do I need to do?

452
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:36,100
All I want is to get Kheetika out of Din's life.

453
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:37,992
And I made it.

454
00:30:37,992 --> 00:30:43,286
Do you mean you accept that she's dating Khun Sira?

455
00:30:43,286 --> 00:30:45,906
I won't accept that.

456
00:30:46,373 --> 00:30:52,860
Then... let me know if you need any help.

457
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:54,960
I have my own plans.

458
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,260
I don't need you.

459
00:30:57,260 --> 00:31:00,100
From now on, you don't have to come to me.

460
00:31:00,100 --> 00:31:02,600
You are of no use to me anymore.

461
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:08,940
Do you think you can get rid of me?

462
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:12,547
There's only interest between us.

463
00:31:12,547 --> 00:31:16,900
But now, you are of no use to me.

464
00:31:16,900 --> 00:31:19,300
I don't have to keep you.

465
00:31:19,300 --> 00:31:21,740
You're thinking of kicking me out?

466
00:31:21,740 --> 00:31:24,540
I'm not going to kick you out now.

467
00:31:24,540 --> 00:31:29,960
But remember, if you get into any trouble at the company,

468
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:32,700
I won't help you.

469
00:31:38,933 --> 00:31:40,533
Okay.

470
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:43,860
I'll keep that in mind.

471
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:55,580
Khun Kansinee is a scary woman.

472
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:58,620
I'm afraid she won't be willing to let it go.

473
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,980
Congratulations on finally being a couple.

474
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:07,300
I never knew when Khun Sira would

475
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:11,600
know how he felt about Khun Kheetika.

476
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:15,780
I want to thank you.

477
00:32:15,780 --> 00:32:17,420
Thank you for enlightening me.

478
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:19,060
You're welcome.

479
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:23,860
Why have his symptoms improved so much?

480
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,725
It's because of love.

481
00:32:25,725 --> 00:32:27,340
Doctor.

482
00:32:27,340 --> 00:32:29,680
When will you stop teasing me?

483
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:33,200
Hey, I'm not teasing you. I'm serious.

484
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:37,520
Khun Sira's symptoms were caused by mental illness.

485
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:40,900
The reason why he consistently had to stay clean was because when he was a child,

486
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:43,060
he had to live in a scary environment.

487
00:32:43,060 --> 00:32:46,420
The things around him cast a shadow on his mind.

488
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:50,480
Your symptoms improved because your mother was around you.

489
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:54,400
Your mother loved you and protected you.

490
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,780
But after my mom disappeared,

491
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:58,740
my symptoms got worse.

492
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:02,580
That was because your protective mechanisms from your mother were gone.

493
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:05,026
So you relapsed.

494
00:33:05,026 --> 00:33:09,860
But don't worry. Now, you have a new protection mechanism.

495
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:12,460
That's Khun Kheetika.

496
00:33:13,555 --> 00:33:16,020
- Me?
- Yes.

497
00:33:16,020 --> 00:33:18,400
When he's around you,

498
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:23,520
he feels safe and comfortable.

499
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:26,880
So he can overcome his fear of dirt.

500
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:29,600
Congratulations, Khun Sira.

501
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:40,460
Thank you, Kanghan.

502
00:33:40,460 --> 00:33:42,980
You brought me good luck.

503
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:46,040
Good luck.

504
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,948
Where did you learn that?

505
00:33:47,948 --> 00:33:50,620
Which movie did you learn that from, Khun Sira?

506
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:54,140
He made fun of me.

507
00:34:02,498 --> 00:34:04,300
Why are you turning on the lights? It's so bright.

508
00:34:04,300 --> 00:34:06,860
Why aren't you going to work today?

509
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:08,820
Are you still upset?

510
00:34:08,820 --> 00:34:12,180
Haven't you accepted Kheetika's relationship with Lom?

511
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,900
I'm just lazy.

512
00:34:17,358 --> 00:34:20,480
It has nothing to do with my brother and Kanghan's relationship.

513
00:34:21,640 --> 00:34:25,220
You love Kheetika so much.

514
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:27,740
Doesn't it hurt to be abandoned like this?

515
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:29,060
No.

516
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:33,432
I am happy to see the two people I love in love.

517
00:34:33,432 --> 00:34:35,713
- Really?
- Really.

518
00:34:35,713 --> 00:34:38,306
Kanghan and I are just friends.

519
00:34:38,306 --> 00:34:39,720
And we will only be friends.

520
00:34:39,720 --> 00:34:43,480
I'm relieved to hear you say that.

521
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:46,262
You like it, don't you?

522
00:34:46,262 --> 00:34:49,200
You've finally separated me from Kanghan.

523
00:34:49,200 --> 00:34:54,340
I hope you will stop meddling in Kanghan and my brother's affairs.

524
00:34:57,580 --> 00:35:02,740
If she doesn't mess with my grandson, I won't do anything to her.

525
00:35:02,740 --> 00:35:04,520
That's good.

526
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:08,720
Let them live a happy life.

527
00:35:08,720 --> 00:35:13,040
I wonder how long

528
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,840
they will be happy,

529
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:18,400
how much will they love each other,

530
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:21,600
and how much will they trust each other.

531
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:23,965
They trust each other very much.

532
00:35:23,965 --> 00:35:27,579
Nothing can destroy their mutual trust.

533
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:32,660
We'll see.

534
00:35:42,180 --> 00:35:45,033
Why did you come back together today?

535
00:35:45,033 --> 00:35:47,146
We ran into each other at the supermarket.

536
00:35:47,146 --> 00:35:49,700
So we came back together.

537
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:52,140
You bought so many things. How about this?

538
00:35:52,140 --> 00:35:54,205
I'll go prepare dinner for you.

539
00:35:54,205 --> 00:35:56,200
Mom, wait.

540
00:35:57,920 --> 00:36:00,680
I have something to tell you.

541
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:04,080
What is it? Just say it.

542
00:36:08,073 --> 00:36:11,333
Now, your symptoms are getting better.

543
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:15,840
I think I'll move back to the apartment.

544
00:36:16,989 --> 00:36:20,620
Why do you want to move back to the apartment?

545
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:28,139
Maybe she's worried that her friend in the apartment misses her.

546
00:36:28,139 --> 00:36:31,899
Maybe she's worried that the people around there...

547
00:36:34,153 --> 00:36:38,660
In that case, can you spend your weekends with me?

548
00:36:39,219 --> 00:36:42,544
Okay. No problem.

549
00:36:42,544 --> 00:36:47,240
Well, Kanghan. My friend called me yesterday.

550
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:50,460
He said you can go there to work when you are ready.

551
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:54,660
You don't have to worry about where you live.

552
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:57,900
Papop's friend has arranged it for you.

553
00:36:57,900 --> 00:37:02,420
I thought about this. I'll come with you.

554
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,980
Mom, you're coming with me?

555
00:37:09,719 --> 00:37:12,100
What about Lung Papop?

556
00:37:12,100 --> 00:37:13,840
Don't worry about me.

557
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:17,240
It's okay if we don't live together.

558
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:20,100
I think you and your mother

559
00:37:20,100 --> 00:37:23,360
should spend more time together.

560
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:26,760
I'm going to live with you for two or three years.

561
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:31,460
Or I'll live with you until you get tired of me and drive me out.

562
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:39,440
I'll go and prepare dinner for you.

563
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:42,680
Give it to me, Khun Hom.

564
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:54,720
You're in trouble.

565
00:37:57,580 --> 00:38:01,180
No one bought it at 3:00. So we bought them all.

566
00:38:01,180 --> 00:38:03,552
Feed me, Darling.

567
00:38:03,552 --> 00:38:07,960
Khun Kheetika. What's wrong? You don't look good.

568
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:11,300
I don't look good?

569
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:14,900
I mean, you look anxious.

570
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:17,040
Your face is pretty.

571
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:21,400
Did you have a fight with Khun Sira?

572
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:26,160
Kirin, what are you talking about? Are you crazy?

573
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:29,800
They are in the infatuation period. How could they fight?

574
00:38:31,553 --> 00:38:34,680
Is it about Khun Sasa?

575
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,200
Did Khun Sasa change his mind?

576
00:38:36,200 --> 00:38:37,900
Stop guessing.

577
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:40,000
I'm worried about work.

578
00:38:40,899 --> 00:38:42,799
What is it?

579
00:38:45,726 --> 00:38:49,246
Kanghan, I want to talk to you.

580
00:38:49,246 --> 00:38:51,080
Come on.

581
00:38:51,620 --> 00:38:53,005
I'll go myself.

582
00:38:53,005 --> 00:38:54,605
Come on.

583
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:59,180
Do you want me to ask Hom out for you?

584
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:01,420
Why don't you call her yourself?

585
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:05,300
If I call her, she won't go out with me.

586
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:09,980
Can you tell me what happened between you?

587
00:39:09,980 --> 00:39:13,540
I want to see Hom. I want her answer first.

588
00:39:13,540 --> 00:39:15,640
Then I'll tell you.

589
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,886
Okay, Kanghan?

590
00:39:19,886 --> 00:39:21,886
Help me.

591
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,120
Okay.

592
00:39:35,700 --> 00:39:38,180
[Kanghan]

593
00:39:45,299 --> 00:39:47,499
Hello.

594
00:39:47,499 --> 00:39:49,073
Hom.

595
00:39:50,987 --> 00:39:52,240
Where are you?

596
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:56,100
I'm at a coffee shop near Khun Sira's apartment.

597
00:39:56,100 --> 00:39:59,960
What are you doing there?

598
00:40:01,180 --> 00:40:03,220
I asked Nannam out.

599
00:40:03,220 --> 00:40:04,540
You asked Nannam out?

600
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:05,580
That dude?

601
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,880
That─

602
00:40:07,680 --> 00:40:10,080
I got his shirt dirty that day.

603
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:12,460
So I bought a new one for him.

604
00:40:13,059 --> 00:40:15,273
What do you want?

605
00:40:15,273 --> 00:40:20,900
I... I'm a little bored. I want to talk to you.

606
00:40:20,900 --> 00:40:22,900
Why call me?

607
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:26,539
Why don't you call your boyfriend?

608
00:40:26,539 --> 00:40:28,339
Yes.

609
00:40:30,500 --> 00:40:32,500
Khun Sira, have you heard the news?

610
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:34,400
Yes.

611
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:35,840
What happened?

612
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:39,480
Why is there a rumor that the chairwoman is going to fire you?

613
00:40:39,480 --> 00:40:42,540
Everybody is talking about it. I just knew it.

614
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:44,869
It's not a rumor, Maha.

615
00:40:44,869 --> 00:40:47,080
The chairwoman has called to inform me

616
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:49,890
that she is going to fire me.

617
00:40:50,860 --> 00:40:53,793
Why?

618
00:40:53,793 --> 00:40:55,820
I don't know.

619
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:58,920
The chairwoman will hold a meeting in a month.

620
00:40:58,920 --> 00:41:02,640
I think she will give the reason.

621
00:41:04,260 --> 00:41:05,980
Khun Kheetika!

622
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:07,660
Something is wrong.

623
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:09,100
What's wrong?

624
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:12,519
I heard that the chairwoman wants to fire Khun Sira.

625
00:41:12,519 --> 00:41:14,119
What?

626
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:22,233
Do you want to fire Khun Lom?

627
00:41:22,233 --> 00:41:25,000
Do I have to answer you?

628
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:27,660
If you are firing him because of me,

629
00:41:27,660 --> 00:41:29,880
you have to answer me.

630
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:34,860
I just learned how important you are.

631
00:41:35,680 --> 00:41:37,840
You are so important that I'll fire Lom for you.

632
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:41,125
It's because he's dating me, right?

633
00:41:41,125 --> 00:41:43,075
- Rossarin.
- Yes.

634
00:41:43,075 --> 00:41:46,733
Go and get Lom to meet me in the conference room.

635
00:41:46,733 --> 00:41:48,180
Khun Premyuda.

636
00:41:48,180 --> 00:41:49,820
- Khun Premyuda!
- Okay.

637
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:51,240
Khun Kheetika.

638
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:53,060
Calm down.

639
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,560
Okay?

640
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:57,280
I'll go get Khun Sira first.

641
00:42:04,409 --> 00:42:05,940
I think you know it, right?

642
00:42:05,940 --> 00:42:10,820
In a month, I'll have Din take over.

643
00:42:10,820 --> 00:42:13,480
The position I prepared for him

644
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:18,700
is the vice chairman of the GU Group, which is your current position.

645
00:42:20,267 --> 00:42:21,940
I know.

646
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:25,667
And you have to leave this position.

647
00:42:25,667 --> 00:42:31,367
I hope you understand my sudden decision to fire you.

648
00:42:31,367 --> 00:42:33,640
I understand.

649
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:36,040
Do you have any questions?

650
00:42:36,040 --> 00:42:37,740
No.

651
00:42:39,232 --> 00:42:41,032
I do.

652
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:49,860
I'm going to write a resignation notice for Khun Sira anyway.

653
00:42:49,860 --> 00:42:54,326
I want to know if I need to write any other notices.

654
00:42:54,326 --> 00:42:56,126
For example,

655
00:42:57,273 --> 00:43:00,993
the notice of Khun Sira's new position after stepping down as vice chairman.

656
00:43:00,993 --> 00:43:02,659
Yes.

657
00:43:02,659 --> 00:43:08,160
After Sira steps down as GU's vice chairman,

658
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:10,220
I'll let him...

659
00:43:11,350 --> 00:43:14,540
replace me as GU's chairman.

660
00:43:20,680 --> 00:43:23,580
Do you want me to replace you as GU's chairman?

661
00:43:24,360 --> 00:43:25,920
Khun Sira, congratulations.

662
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:29,520
You're going to be GU's chairman.

663
00:43:31,305 --> 00:43:34,640
Why do you suddenly want me to be the chairman?

664
00:43:34,640 --> 00:43:37,420
I'm tired. I want to rest.

665
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:41,200
You've been doing great,

666
00:43:41,999 --> 00:43:45,840
especially in the recent task.

667
00:43:46,460 --> 00:43:48,780
I'm proud of you.

668
00:43:48,780 --> 00:43:52,925
I'm sorry, Ms. Chairwoman. What task?

669
00:43:53,560 --> 00:43:58,520
The task I asked you to make Kheetika fall in love with you

670
00:43:58,520 --> 00:44:00,860
and get her out of Din's life.

671
00:44:00,860 --> 00:44:02,680
You did a good job.

672
00:44:02,680 --> 00:44:05,440
Kheetika loves you very much now.

673
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:08,480
You can go out with Kheetika for another month or two.

674
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:10,160
Then you can get rid of her.

675
00:44:10,160 --> 00:44:12,880
I'll let you make the decision.

676
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:19,498
Ms. Chairwoman, I think you misunderstood Kheetika and me.

677
00:44:19,498 --> 00:44:21,198
Enough.

678
00:44:21,740 --> 00:44:23,820
I have other things to do.

679
00:44:24,420 --> 00:44:26,720
You'll take care of it.

680
00:44:29,080 --> 00:44:32,620
I'm sorry. I want to explain what's going on with Kheetika and me.

681
00:44:36,211 --> 00:44:38,160
- Ms. Chairwoman.
- Khun Lom.

682
00:44:38,880 --> 00:44:42,740
Have you really been fired?

683
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:46,000
I'll make it clear to the chairwoman first.

684
00:44:48,833 --> 00:44:51,600
Darling, what's going on?

685
00:44:51,600 --> 00:44:54,200
Has Khun Sira really been fired?

686
00:44:55,020 --> 00:44:58,940
It's true Khun Sira was fired from the position of vice chairman.

687
00:44:58,940 --> 00:45:03,200
Khun Sira has been working hard.

688
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:05,780
Calm down, Khun Pa.

689
00:45:05,780 --> 00:45:09,933
The chairwoman fired Khun Sira from the position of vice chairman.

690
00:45:09,933 --> 00:45:12,653
Because she wants to make him GU's chairman.

691
00:45:14,100 --> 00:45:17,300
Did Khun Premyuda make him the chairman?

692
00:45:17,300 --> 00:45:19,505
Isn't that good news, Darling?

693
00:45:19,505 --> 00:45:20,606
Yes.

694
00:45:20,606 --> 00:45:22,760
Did she give a reason?

695
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:24,760
She didn't.

696
00:45:26,500 --> 00:45:28,300
We should celebrate it.

697
00:45:28,300 --> 00:45:31,620
Let's celebrate. He's becoming chairman.

698
00:45:35,560 --> 00:45:38,820
P'Hom, you don't have to waste money and buy a new shirt for me.

699
00:45:38,820 --> 00:45:41,920
It can be washed clean.

700
00:45:41,920 --> 00:45:43,460
But I feel bad about it.

701
00:45:43,460 --> 00:45:48,880
When I damage someone's property and I don't compensate them, I feel guilty.

702
00:45:48,880 --> 00:45:54,998
If I want new clothes, I should hit you more.

703
00:45:54,998 --> 00:45:57,380
So I will have plenty of new clothes.

704
00:45:58,519 --> 00:46:00,380
Do you want me to get this one dirty, too?

705
00:46:00,380 --> 00:46:02,473
Last time, it was lipstick.

706
00:46:02,473 --> 00:46:05,198
This time, let me use hot tea.

707
00:46:05,198 --> 00:46:07,098
I am kidding.

708
00:46:10,777 --> 00:46:14,178
If you like to buy clothes for others, buy me some, too.

709
00:46:14,880 --> 00:46:16,580
How did you get here?

710
00:46:17,433 --> 00:46:19,133
By car.

711
00:46:20,040 --> 00:46:22,960
I'm not asking how you got here.

712
00:46:22,960 --> 00:46:25,520
How did you know I was here?

713
00:46:26,640 --> 00:46:28,906
Do you like old women?

714
00:46:28,906 --> 00:46:32,380
You missed Kanghan. Then you went to her sister.

715
00:46:32,380 --> 00:46:35,040
P'Hom and I just know each other.

716
00:46:35,040 --> 00:46:39,720
Before you say anything, please consider her feelings.

717
00:46:39,720 --> 00:46:42,226
You speak like a gentleman.

718
00:46:42,226 --> 00:46:45,609
Do you like such a gentle and sweet man?

719
00:46:47,479 --> 00:46:51,279
Yes. I like this kind of man.

720
00:46:52,460 --> 00:46:56,440
Get away. Please don't disturb my private life.

721
00:46:58,139 --> 00:46:59,860
I can go away.

722
00:47:00,906 --> 00:47:04,475
But you have to come with me because I have something to tell you.

723
00:47:06,032 --> 00:47:07,398
Let go.

724
00:47:07,398 --> 00:47:10,647
Din. You are hurting me. Let go.

725
00:47:10,647 --> 00:47:14,740
I think if P'Hom doesn't want to go with you,

726
00:47:14,740 --> 00:47:17,200
you should let go of your hand.

727
00:47:18,540 --> 00:47:21,986
You should let go of your hand,

728
00:47:21,986 --> 00:47:26,106
because I have something to say to my girlfriend.

729
00:47:27,620 --> 00:47:29,900
When did I become your girlfriend?

730
00:47:31,653 --> 00:47:36,373
Do you want me to tell him what happened that night?

731
00:47:48,393 --> 00:47:50,393
What do you want to say?

732
00:47:50,393 --> 00:47:52,440
Do you like that dude?

733
00:47:52,440 --> 00:47:55,500
Be honest. Don't be sarcastic.

734
00:47:56,373 --> 00:47:57,820
No.

735
00:47:57,820 --> 00:47:59,760
You're not lying to me. Right?

736
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:01,820
Why should I lie to you?

737
00:48:01,820 --> 00:48:04,466
Is that all you want to ask?

738
00:48:04,466 --> 00:48:07,106
I want to ask you something.

739
00:48:08,420 --> 00:48:10,740
But before you answer me,

740
00:48:10,740 --> 00:48:15,000
you have to promise that you will answer sensibly.

741
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:17,493
No need to rush. Take your time.

742
00:48:17,493 --> 00:48:19,193
Say what's on your mind.

743
00:48:19,193 --> 00:48:22,660
Don't be sarcastic. And follow your heart.

744
00:48:27,520 --> 00:48:30,920
If you don't ask, I'll leave.

745
00:48:30,940 --> 00:48:32,987
Do you want to go out with me?

746
00:48:37,598 --> 00:48:39,098
I...

747
00:48:40,115 --> 00:48:42,900
I want to take responsibility for what happened that night.

748
00:48:50,419 --> 00:48:52,119
It's not necessary.

749
00:48:53,260 --> 00:48:56,680
I told you not to rush to answer. Take your time.

750
00:48:56,680 --> 00:49:00,610
Do you want to go out with me just because you feel guilty?

751
00:49:00,610 --> 00:49:02,859
If that's the case, you don't have to.

752
00:49:02,859 --> 00:49:06,250
Two people should date out of affection for each other,

753
00:49:06,250 --> 00:49:09,060
not about guilty feelings and taking responsibility.

754
00:49:09,680 --> 00:49:11,580
What if I tell you...

755
00:49:13,140 --> 00:49:17,020
I want to go out with you not just out of guilt...

756
00:49:19,961 --> 00:49:22,001
but because I'm attracted to you?

757
00:49:22,001 --> 00:49:23,678
I want to have you by my side.

758
00:49:23,678 --> 00:49:27,024
I want to hang out with you, go to the movies, and go to dinner.

759
00:49:28,239 --> 00:49:30,239
Are you okay with it?

760
00:49:31,933 --> 00:49:34,920
Why should I go according to these words?

761
00:49:38,180 --> 00:49:40,020
Are you really stuck in traffic?

762
00:49:40,020 --> 00:49:42,380
I thought about that all night.

763
00:49:43,448 --> 00:49:45,381
Did you figure it out yourself?

764
00:49:47,346 --> 00:49:50,952
It's for chasing you. I had to figure it out myself.

765
00:49:52,999 --> 00:49:54,699
So...

766
00:49:56,180 --> 00:49:58,360
Do you want to go out with me?

767
00:50:04,420 --> 00:50:05,699
Are you sure?

768
00:50:05,699 --> 00:50:07,840
Do you really want to go out with me?

769
00:50:08,690 --> 00:50:09,810
Yeah.

770
00:50:18,380 --> 00:50:20,640
I'll think about it.

771
00:50:35,700 --> 00:50:37,640
Darling, come with me.

772
00:50:38,480 --> 00:50:40,780
What do you want? What's wrong, Darling?

773
00:50:40,780 --> 00:50:42,620
Darling, I don't know what to do.

774
00:50:42,620 --> 00:50:44,460
I feel so bad.

775
00:50:44,460 --> 00:50:46,680
What's wrong?

776
00:50:50,780 --> 00:50:53,400
It's Khun Kheetika.

777
00:50:58,420 --> 00:51:00,175
Maha isn't answering his phone.

778
00:51:00,175 --> 00:51:02,349
Khun Lom isn't answering his phone either.

779
00:51:04,532 --> 00:51:06,560
She's calling me again.
[Khun Kheetika]

780
00:51:06,560 --> 00:51:08,140
Pick up, Darling.

781
00:51:08,140 --> 00:51:10,620
What if Khun Kheetika has an emergency?

782
00:51:11,480 --> 00:51:13,280
Pick up.

783
00:51:18,705 --> 00:51:20,540
Maha.

784
00:51:20,540 --> 00:51:22,560
Hello, Khun Kheetika.

785
00:51:23,260 --> 00:51:24,960
Have you seen Lom?

786
00:51:24,960 --> 00:51:27,720
I can't find him.

787
00:51:28,820 --> 00:51:31,280
I haven't seen him.

788
00:51:35,193 --> 00:51:36,340
Maha.

789
00:51:36,340 --> 00:51:38,620
